# Munder Difflin Paper Co - Multi Agent System

## What this does

This is my multi agent system for the Munder Difflin paper company project. 
The system takes customer requests for paper supplies and tries to fufill them 
using our inventory database. If somthing isnt available it tells the customer.

## Agents

### Orchestrator
The main agent that recives customer requests and decides what to do.
It passes the inventory list to each request so the other agents know 
what items we actually have in stock.

### Inventory Agent
Checks whats in stock. Has tools for:
- check_inventory - gets everything in stock on a given date
- get_available_items - returns a formatted list of stock
- check_item_stock - checks a specific item
- check_delivery_date - estimates when supplier can deliver

### Quoting Agent
Looks at past quotes and checks cash balance before approving orders.
Tools: get_quote_history, get_current_cash

### Ordering Agent
Actually places the orders and records them in the database.
Tool: fulfill_order - this one does fuzzy matching on item names 
so "A4 glossy paper" matches to "Glossy paper" in our db.

## How it runs

1. Load the database with inventory and past quotes
2. Read quote_requests_sample.csv 
3. For each request, pass it to the orchestrator with todays inventory
4. Orchestrator delegates to the right agents
5. Results get saved to test_results.csv

## Results

Started with $45,059 cash. After processing all the requests 
ended up with $45,154 so we made about $95 in sales.

Some orders couldnt be fullfilled because customers asked for things 
like balloons and streamers which we dont sell. Those got rejected 
with an explanation.

## Framework used

smolagents with OpenAI gpt-4o-mini